snippet.title: v7.7 Drudging, Drifting, Dreaming Trailer — Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd v7.7 Drudging, Drifting, Dreaming coming soon! Theresa's new S-rank battlesuit Schicksal's Imperative debuts!
Part 2 Main Story Chapter IV A Shore Under Watch and featured event Born From A Dream will also be available. Stay tuned!

Voice Artists:
Dreamseeker: Yuki Nakashima
Theresa: Yukari Tamura
